column52: We all know Johnnys late mother’s yorkie Boo, who Johnny took back into his own care, was taken by Amber during their divorce settlement in 2017. column52: We all know Johnnys late mother’s yorkie Boo, who Johnny took back into his own care, was taken by Amber during their divorce settlement in 2017. In which Amber took custody of her dog Pistol and Johnny’s late mother’s dog, Boo. It was later known that Amber had given Boo to her father, David Heard who also exposed for abusing dogs in cage fights. This petition is to demand David Heard to tell us where Boo is and if she has been abused!! This is psychological torture and if Boo is not alive, we have more a reason to think that Amber is truly what the world sees her to be— a pathological liar. #WhereIsBoo
